      "widgets_values": [
        "Built to work with Z Image Turbo (and custom checkpoints)\n\n*MODEL*\nhttps://civitai.com/models/2168935/z-image-turbo?modelVersionId=2442439\n\n--DOWNLOADS FOR WORKFLOW--\n\n*UPSCALERS*\nhttps://civitai.com/models/116225/4x-ultrasharp\n\nhttps://huggingface.co/notkenski/upscalers/blob/main/1xSkinContrast-High-SuperUltraCompact.pth\n\n\n---------------------\n\n*RECOMMEND SETTINGS*\nSampler: Euler or reds_multistep with \nScheduler: Simple or Beta\n\nSteps: 9~11\n\nCFG Scale: 1\n\n**My prompt structure (optional)**\n\nSTRUCTURE:\n\nCONCEPT & MEDIUM: Start with the type of image. Mention the core theme or event.\n\nSUBJECT DESCRIPTION: Young woman, facial expression, hair details, face details, makeup. Crucially, describe their gaze. \n\nACTION & INTERACTION: Describe exactly what the person is doing. What are they holding? How are they standing? Describe the interaction with objects.\n\nAPPAREL: Detail the clothing (fabric, color, fit) and accessories.\n\nENVIRONMENT & FOREGROUND: Describe objects immediately around the person.\n\nBACKGROUND & LIGHTING: Describe the setting (location, weather, landmarks), depth of field (bokeh), and the quality of light.\n"
      ]
    }
